{"tid":896444,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉湖山莊兩房戶440萬元沽  實用呎價失守1萬元關","createTime":"2018-11-10T04:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T13:39:38.000Z","uid":221051,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"55010e22df1d219d94510071e2b83dd8a76f51d2","tid":896444,"uid":221051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:35:45.000Z","msg":"中原營業經理葉浩麟表示，樓市逐步降溫，天水圍嘉湖山莊部分業主面對現實減價，帶動近日睇樓量回升，屋苑11月份暫錄得5宗買賣成交。<br />\n<br />\n葉指，屋苑新近錄得首宗兩房成交，為賞湖居5座中層F室，實用面積449方呎，兩房間隔，向東南，望街景，以440萬港元獲承接，實用呎價9,800元，失守1萬元關口。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，買家為天水圍分支家庭，眼見樓價由高位回調20%，當機立斷買入自住組織家庭。原業主於2009年10月以138萬買入單位，現轉手帳面獲利302萬元，升值3倍。"},{"pid":"845a5ab32d1a54b5e71722723d1ccc36f081739a","tid":896444,"uid":46042,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:36:32.000Z","msg":"新界唔計"},{"pid":"cd9db43056323c95c6cf378786f20aaef3f70991","tid":896444,"uid":88896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:37:46.000Z","msg":"升值三倍 唔計"},{"pid":"b62f95163039b19b4bfb1190283fd6a8256060f1","tid":896444,"uid":76745,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:37:52.000Z","msg":"工作太忙 住太大沒意思<br />\n440萬買寶星算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f09538bc760618a135b6464cd0621c308a8ecd","tid":896444,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75ae91d